      "title": "Measure valued solutions to conservation laws motivated by traffic modelling",
      "abstract": "Motivated by a traffic model, we study a conservation law whose solutions naturally need to be bounded Radon measures. We investigate the relations between this equation and finite systems of conservation laws that converge to it."
